description:
It is based on SMPC technology and anonymous biometrics. It allows you to manage digital assets without a Private Key. It is replaced with an encrypted set of secrets, distributed between your device and professional security provider. This means that:

- nobody except you has access to the funds;

- your funds will still be safe even if your device is hacked;

- even if you lose all credentials you can recover your wallet using your face.

This makes Spatium the safest and easiest crypto wallet no matter if you haven`t heard anything about Bitcoin before, or if you are an experienced crypto geek.
